@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xvgann(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.89 - (tmp + 0.73 / v0 + 0.60)) / ((v1 + 0.85 - v1 + 0.42) + (tmp + 0.55 * tmp + 0.46)))
    v1 = 0.64
    tmp = (v1 + wp.exp((tmp + 0.53 / tmp + 0.82)))
    v0 = (v1 / ((v2 + 0.50 + v1 + 0.75) / (tmp + 0.77 / v0 + 0.83)))
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = (wp.abs(tmp) * ((v2 + 0.08 / tmp + 0.03) * (v0 + 0.40 - v0 + 0.18)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.38) + wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.69)))
    data[tid] = v0
